      "value": "Fowler's third Durham account-roll volume continues the Bursars' accounts and adds coal-mine accounts, extracts from post-Dissolution Cathedral Treasurers' books, and a miscellany of bills, vouchers, receipts, memoranda, inventories, and account fragments. The selected records document central finance, estates, rents, debts, mining, coal transport, labor, wages, construction, church fabric, household and institutional supplies, prices, travel, and material culture from 1293 to 1597.",
      "language": "eng",
      "scope": {
        "kind": "whole"
      },
      "evidence_ids": [
        "evidence:cme00048-fowler-volume3",
        "evidence:cme00048-fowler-introduction",
        "evidence:cme00048-durham-catalog"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "summary:contents",
      "type": "contents_note",
      "value": "The encoded body has four edition-defined sections: Bursars, 152 direct DIV2 units on pp. 577–707; coal mines, 18 on pp. 708–713; Treasurer's books, 10 on pp. 714–717; and Miscellanea, 68 on pp. 718–743. The XML includes the edition title page but omits the preface, contents, general index, amendments and corrigenda, subject lists, unexplained-word list, works cited, glossary, retrospective introduction, and society matter.",
      "language": "eng",
      "scope": {
        "kind": "whole"
      },
      "evidence_ids": [
        "evidence:cme00048-structure",
        "evidence:cme00048-fowler-volume3"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "summary:cataloging-scope",
      "type": "scope_note",
      "value": "The 248 XML DIV2 containers represent Fowler's editorial sequence, not a physical-document inventory. Current official catalogs establish 233 exact public Durham IIIF objects, plus separately identifiable non-public copies, books, bills, and fragments. Duplicate copies and drafts, dorse texts, aggregate multi-bill manifests, separately preserved bills, and incomplete face-only inventories require a many-to-many crosswalk.",
      "language": "eng",
      "scope": {
        "kind": "whole"
      },
      "evidence_ids": [
        "evidence:cme00048-structure",
        "evidence:cme00048-durham-catalog",
        "evidence:cme00048-durham-iiif"
      ]
    }
  ],
